🧠 Project Overview

In this project, we implemented monitoring and alerting using AWS CloudWatch and Terraform.

The goal was to create an automated alarm that monitors CPU utilization of an EC2 instance and triggers when usage exceeds a defined threshold.

This simulates a real-world DevOps monitoring setup where teams detect performance issues before they impact users.

🎯 Objective

Using Terraform, we:

Created a CloudWatch alarm named datacenter-alarm
Monitored EC2 CPU utilization
Triggered alarm when CPU > 80%
Set evaluation period to 5 minutes (300 seconds)
Used a single evaluation period
Fully automated infrastructure using IaC
