⚠️ Challenges Encountered

During implementation, we discovered:

No EC2 instances were visible in the AWS environment
Terraform data.aws_instance lookup failed
Required adjustment to direct instance reference
Key Debugging Insight:

Always validate existing infrastructure before using Terraform data sources.

